column5: Buying back some stuff today Focusing on stocks that seem to be in the strongest position to run in the short term Still keeping a lot of cash on the side My favs right now CWBHF ZEN ADBE EW VEEV I did keep CRON during the downturn since I was in the red and was confident it would come back at some point Even though it is up 8 st the moment I still am feeling cautious I am happy to see the spike today And a lot of bullish signals I guess it depends on whether holders will choose to take profits or hold for awhile
